DEVICE: Omi AI Wearable — Full Reference Descriptor

-- OVERALL FORM --
Shape:    Circular disc, lens/pebble profile
          Symmetrically domed on both faces (top dome slightly more pronounced)
          Thin dark machined groove running around the full equator
Size:     ~25mm diameter, ~14mm total height
          Comparable to a large coat button or a stack of 3 coins
          Significantly smaller than a smartphone — fits on a fingertip

-- SURFACE & MATERIAL --
Texture:  Matte sandblasted metal finish — fine granular texture, not glossy
          Micro-sparkle visible under direct light
Color:    Warm silver-grey (gunmetal tone, not bright chrome)
          Subtle gradient from lighter dome center to slightly darker edges
Finish:   Single continuous curved surface — no seams, no ports, no buttons
          One face only: contains the LED recess (see below)
          Opposite face: identical dome, completely clean — no markings

-- LED (front face only) --
Type:     Single point-source LED, deep-recessed into the surface
          Does NOT protrude — sits flush or slightly below surface level
          Appears as a small glowing eye embedded in the metal
Shape:    Tiny oval/elliptical aperture (~2-3mm), like a narrow slit or pupil
Position: Slightly off-center toward upper area of the front dome face
Color:    Bright electric blue when active — soft halo glow diffused by recess
          No LED visible from back, sides, or at sharp angles

-- RUBBER CASE / HOLDER --
Material: Transparent frosted TPU rubber — slight milky clarity, not fully clear
Shape:    Ring/halo — wraps equator groove only, does not cover either dome face
Width:    ~4-5mm visible band, sits proud of the metal shell by ~1-2mm
Profile:  Rounded cross-section, smooth surface
Tab:      Single small loop protrusion at 12 o'clock position
          Hollow eyelet through which a cord or chain is threaded
          Same frosted TPU material, seamlessly integrated

-- WEARING --
Cord:     Thin flat black rubber/silicone cord
          Threaded through the TPU tab eyelet
          Worn as a minimal pendant, device hangs face-forward on chest
